{"tid":1687080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都話助攻","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T15:38:35.000Z","uid":334282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cec9bec156277717a6b1cb0e666b03d30dc8bb72","tid":1687080,"uid":334282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"其實個個都成日見到政府警狗做幾多仆街野，單單野都話助攻，單單野都話核彈。但係講完之後呢，助左去邊？警狗無屌錯，我地個個都企係到乜9都唔做，留兩個comment 講下助攻、核彈就算，人影都唔見埋，革命靠咁樣既我地真係死得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要做既野，係文攻武衛，而唔係坐以待斃。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">長話短說，總之 11月2號 維園見。唔好令逝世既受傷既被捕既手足失望。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d25466574f662b339075503495e0a41ec4e6ab0","tid":1687080,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSO2Qd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSO2Qd4.gif&h=b2e98198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"926506c24f642f5262159b14e2b1e283cd0a8d31","tid":1687080,"uid":334282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"dd2d0077b93d084631c074c841a81e2f2263b403","tid":1687080,"uid":334282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"}]}